snippet.title: Meet CarryMinati | Episode 89
snippet.description:
YouTube Channel: https://m.youtube.com/@CarryMinati 

Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

snippet.title: Holi Returns | Ashish chanchlani
snippet.description:
Download Probo & Earn Money:- https://probo-in.onelink.me/1kre/AshishChanchlaniVines


#AshishChanchlani #HoliReturns #Acvians 
Haan toh suno tum log 
Main pehle hi bata du ye video legit tumhari kasam humne kal hi khatam ki hai😂😂
Ek side main shoot kar raha thaa dusre side kunal scene laptop mein edit kar raha tha
Puri raat hum sab office mein hi soye hai (tension nahi lo sirf soye hai)
Haan toh point pe aate hai
Aa gayi hai
Aap sab
Seth log
Acvians ki special demand par humari purani style mein
HOLI RETURNS
Jaldi se jaldi pura video dekho aur apna
Sabse fav dialogue aur scene comment karo
Main tum sab ke comments padhta hu
(Pata chal hi gaya hoga islie toh itna jaldi video banayi)
Chalo
Abhi video ke production ki baat karte hai
Ye video mein main hu kunal hai jo paisa hi bas teacher driver watchman ke role ke lie hua tha
Jadoo aka akash dodeja ko maine nashe waala character islie diya cause uske lie shoot easy tha
Simran aayi ek scene ke lie usme bhi dhoop mein nakhre
Bhavika ko bahut thank you bechari sirf free ke khaane ke lie role karti
Rohit ke hoet pehli baar kaale nai safed pade
Tanish aur grishim jinhone bathroom mein make out kiya
Jashan jo boat mein box fek ke aaya
Ritesh jo rohit se better jokes maarta hai
Paras saale ko playground jaane ka ghamand aa gaya hai
Animesh apna nanga avatar
Jagu jiske nukeele samose maine khaye
Aur baaki pyaate actors jinhone humare video mein chaar chand laga diye: piyush,Rocky,Ishaan,dhiraj,Abhishek, Loveya tanish,piyush,sahil, vishal & angad

Production apna bache logo ne bahut acha sambhala lekin sabse badiya jashan, ritesh aur tanni ne samabhala
Becharo ko ek saath bukhar padh gaya
Par ye bukhar ek dusre ko kiss karne ki wajah se aaya

Vfx : Mere pyaare dulare AMAN VFX GUY ne kiya hai
Us bechare ko maine sirf 2 redbull di iss scene ke lie

Dop apna topi ke saath paida hua Sidharth Kedare
Editing grishi, ritesh tanni aur kunal ne ki 
Lekin asli haath toh mera hi hota hai huihuihui

Background score : Mere pyaare bhai Abhishek-Vivek ne kiya hai unka channel dekho bahut talented hai

And finally sabse zyada special thanks to Sunil Talreja uncle, we love youuu
(SUNRISE INTERNATIONAL SCHOOL UNKA HAI❤️🙏)

Lyrics:
Chamkeela angeelesi O Vadhiney
Chaaku lekkundetodey O Vadhiney
Kandlaku ainaa betti kaththoley
Kannetla koduthundeney
Sinigina baneeneysi O Vadhiney
Nattintla koosuntadey O Vadhiney
Maasina lungi yesi ippudu
Manchamlaney pantadey

Pendlaina koththala aththarlu poosinney
Nee seera singhulu patti yenakenaka thiriginney
Muddhulisthundey poolu thesthundey
Sakkera lekka nee maatalumtundey
Maarey nee theeru perigey nee noru
Mandhukalavaataithiney

Kadupula intha bosi O Vadhiney
Koduthadey bandakesi O Vadhiney
Amavaasa punnaaniko atlatla
Akkaraku pakkakoththadammo

Kanta neeranna pettakunda santibidda lekka
Ninnu Aluguthuntey boodharakiyyaledhaa
Nuvvu seetiki maatiki gintha dhaanni ganthajeysi
Ijjathamtha bazaarlesthalevaa

Yem gaali sokeno…veenneththi thirigeno..
Paathabaddanemo chethanaitha ledho
Ultaa nannitla mandhi mungatla badhnaam jeththadu

Noridisi adagadhuraa baammardhi
Cheppindhi cheyyadhuraa baammardhi
Pakkintla koosuntadhi naa meedha
Chaadeelu chepthuntadhi
Naa gonthu kosindrantu bammardhi
Sokaalu peduthuntadhi bammardhi
Muchchatlu jeppabothey meeyakka
Moothantha thipputhuntadhi

Seekatla unnaa vaakitla unnaa
Kantiki reppoley kaasthadu mogadu
Yentha lollaina nuvventa untey
Yedhuru nilsi vaadu gelsi vasthaadu
Gosalni joostha unnaa yedhainaa
Gundella dhaasthaaduley
Nee bottu nee gaajuley yenthainaa
Vaani paanaaluley

snippet.title: Meeting में Jetha ने मारी सभी को पिचकारी | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Holi Special
snippet.description:
Jetha makes fun of Iyer as he is unable to understand Hindi. Jetha then asks Iyer to learn Hindi and Gujarati language, as it will be of great help to both of them. However, Iyer takes Jetha’s advice as an offence. The fight escalates and every member of Gokuldham Society then declares that they will speak in their respective language. As a result, the Undhiyu party gets cancelled.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast – Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By – Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #SonyPAL #holi #holispecial #happyholi 

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Watch all the 'Holi Special' clips especially curated for you:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G0mUUtCU8U1fh6FBZKC6ahg

snippet.description:

Tere Bin Episode 21 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 8th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 22 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 9th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 23 Teaser - 9th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 23 Teaser - 9th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

#yumnazaidi

snippet.title: iPhone 15 Pro Is Coming With Ultimate Features🔥🔥🔥
snippet.description:
Namaskar Dosto, aaj ke video mai humne baat ki hai Upcoming and most waited iPhone 15 ke baare mai. Doston, iPhone 15 aane waale hai humare paas September 2023 mai. Humare paas aane wale hain 4 models iPhone 15, iPhone 15 Plus, iPhone 15 Pro, iPhone 15 Pro Ultra and hume dekhne ko mil sakte hain kuch changes jaise Pro models aa sakte hain Apple ki A17 Bionic Chip ke sath, Periscope mechanism waala zoom feature aa sakta hai camera mai saath mein hum 8K video record kar paayenge, aur Solid State Buttons bhi aa sakte hai. iPhone 15 mai hum Type-C Charging bhi milne waala hai. Pro models mai hume milne waala hai ek titanium frame. Video ko Like karke comment karke zarur batana aap kitna excited hain iPhone 15 ke Launch ko leke?

snippet.description:
"Rang Barse" a popular Holi song sung by Amitabh Bachchan that has become an integral part of the Indian festival of colors. Its lively beats and playful lyrics celebrate the spirit of Holi, encouraging people to let go and have fun. The song's iconic status has made it a must-play during Holi festivities. Let's groove to the song now!

Song: Rang Barse
Film: Silsila
Artist: Amitabh Bachhan
Music Director: Shiv-Hari
Lyricist: Harivansh Rai Bachchan
Film Star: Amitabh Bachchan, Jaya Bachchan, Sanjeev Kumar, Rekha, Shashi Kapoor
Director: Yash Chopra

Lyrics:

Rang barase bhige
Chunarawali rang barase

Are kaine maari pichakaari
Tori bhigi angiyaa
O rangrasiya rangrasiya

Rang barase
Rang barase bhige
Chunarawali rang barase
O rang barase bhige
Chunarawali rang barase

Ha rang barase bhige
Chunarawali rang barase

Sone ki thaali mein jonaa parosa
Are sone ki thaali mein
Haan sone ki thaali
Mein jonaa parosa
Are khaae gori kaa
Yaar balam tarase
Rang barase holi hai!
O rang barase bhige
Chunarawali rang barase

Laungaa ilaayachi kaa are
Laungaa ilaayachi kaa bhai
Laungaa ilaayachi kaa haan
Are laungaa ilaayachi
Kaa bidaa lagaya
Haan laungaa ilaayachi kaa
Haan laungaa ilaayachi
Kaa bidaa lagaya
Chaabe gori kaa yaar
Balam tarase rang barase
Holi hai!

O rang barase bhige
Chunarawali rang barase
O rang barase bhige
Chunarawali rang barase
O rang barase bhige
Chunarawali rang barase

Are belaa chameli kaa sej bichhaya
Belaa chameli kaa sej bichhaya
Are belaa chameli
Kaa sej bichhaya
Are belaa chameli kaa
Haan belaa chameli
Kaa sej bichhaya
Soe gori kaa yaar balam
Tarase rang barase holi hai!

O rang barase bhige
Chunarawali rang barase... (6)

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3714 - 9 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3714: Hungame Vaali Holi
--------------------------------------------------------
On the auspicious festival, "Holi," Bhide writes a special "Suvichaar" to inspire and motivate everybody. As Bhide was busy jotting down his thoughts, Tapu smeared him with a splash of Gulal. Bhide gets a little annoyed, but Tapu and Tapu Sena manage to escape because of the festive mood. When Sodhi sees Bhide, he complains that he had already played Holi without him. Bhide tells him that it was Tapu who had put colors on him. Anyway, while everyone starts enjoying the occasion, Bhide feels an itchy reaction on his back. Did Tapu intentionally put something in the colors for fun? Will Bhide like Tapu's frivolous deed? Stay tuned! 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3714, 9 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000212815

snippet.title: Gokuldham वाले खेलने लगे Ketchup और Besan से Holi! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Holi Special
snippet.description:
Popatlal tries to make fried snacks for the breakfast but he notices that he does not have any tomato sauce in the house to have with the snacks. So, he tries to call Abdul, but Abdul does not pick his phone up. Popatlal then comes out on the balcony of his house and shouts Abdul’s name. Bhide and others notice Popatlal shouting so they ask him the reason for his yelling. Popatlal tells everyone that he has made some fried snacks and he needs some tomato sauce to eat with them. Bhide tells Popatlal that he will give him the tomato sauce. Later, Bhide goes to Popatlal with a bottle of tomato sauce and leaves. When Popatlal notices that the tomato is expired he comes downstairs screaming Bhide’s name. What will Popatlal do now? Let’s find out.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast – Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By – Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #SonyPAL #holi #holispecial #happyholi 

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Watch all the 'Holi Special' clips especially curated for you:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G0mUUtCU8U1fh6FBZKC6ahg

snippet.title: Peshawar Zalmi vs Quetta Gladiators | Highlights | Pakistan Super League | 8th March 2023
snippet.description:
Peshawar Zalmi batted superbly and posted a mammoth total of 240 runs at the end of their innings. Captain Babar Azam was the star with a century to his name. Peshawar Zalmi looked like the winners even before Quetta Gladiators came to bat, however, Jason Roy had other plans. The opener looked unstoppable as he was dealing in boundaries and went on to make 145 runs from just 63 deliveries. This power-packed knock helped the Quetta Gladiators to win by 8 wickets and 10 balls remaining. 
.
.

snippet.title: Women Task Force | Purvi Gives A Tough Fight Against An 'Anaconda Man' | CID | 7 March 2023
snippet.description:
Purvi fought the case to save many people from a dangerous snake. The power of the snake was misused by people who took the lives of many people. Purvi with other officers gave a tough fight and helped them to save mankind.  Will team CID be successful in saving their lives? To know more watch the full episode.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode No:  1339
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh
 
#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #CID Nostalgia #LIVCrime #NewCID #LatestCID #Crime

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: "मैं मर भी जाती तो मां-बाप को कोई गम नहीं होता" | Savita Pradhan | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Savita जी की तरह कड़ी मेहनत और ज़िद से करें अपना हर सपना पूरा: https://joshskills.app.link/ZxGvfIxQWxb

Savita ji was born in a tribal family in a small village "Mandi" of Madhya Pradesh, she was brought up in a very poor family. Savita ji used to walk with a limp in her childhood. But his courage never stopped walking. I was the first girl in this village who passed 12th. But life's difficulties had just begun. After marriage, they were tortured a lot, killed, beaten, and kept hungry. It had come to the point that he had even thought of hanging himself. But the zeal to stand again takes birth in her and today she is working as the Municipal Commissioner.

Today Savita ji will tell her success story through Josh Talks. So do watch this Motivational video of Josh Talks today.

Savita जी का जन्म Madhya Pradesh के एक छोटे से गांव “मंडी” में आदिवासी परिवार में हुआ था, इनका पालन पोषण बहुत ही गरीब परिवार में रहा। सविता जी बचपन में लंगड़ा कर चलती थी। मगर इनके हौसले ने चलना कभी नहीं छोड़ा। यह गांव में मैं पहली लड़की थी जिसने 12th pass किया था। मगर ज़िंदगी की मुश्किलें अभी शुरू हुई थीं। शादी के बाद इनके साथ बहुत अत्याचार हुए, मारा गया, पीटा गया, भूखा रखा गया। नौबत यह आ गयी थी कि इन्होंने फांसी तक लगाने की सोच ली थी। मगर फिर से खड़े होने का जोश इनके अंदर जन्म लेता है और आज यह नगर निगम कमिश्नर के पद के रूप में काम कर रही हैं। 

आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से Savita जी सुनाएंगी अपनी Success story. तो जोश Talks की इस Motivational video को आज ज़रूर देखें. 

#JoshTalksHindi #SavitaJoshTalks #womenmotivationshorts 

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JoshTalksHindi​ 
► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHi... 

-----**DISCLAIMER**----- 
All of the views and work outside the pretext of the video of the speaker, are his/ her own, and Josh Talks, by any means, does not support them directly or indirectly and neither is it liable for it. Viewers are requested to use their own discretion while viewing the content and focus on the entirety of the story rather than finding inferences in its parts. Josh Talks by any means, does not further or amplify any specific ideology or propaganda.

Ho Bhari Mohabbat Dekho. Dekho har baat mein 

Kuch itne haseen hain hum, haseen hum sath mein 
 
Dhoop lage jo tumko sar Par chaon ban jayege 
Kaanto Par chalna bejijhak tere paon ban jayege  
Haar kar na haare waisi haar jaisa hota hai 
Ye jaana tumse mil kar jaana pyar Kaisa hota hai  
Ho Chand chamakta jaise, jaise Ho raat mein 
  
Kuch itne haseen hain hum, haseen hum sath mein 
 
Sada hi sath rahege, samay ka paimaan hai 
Ishq bhara mausam mein mausam bhi bayimaan hai 
Mitti aur khusbhu jaise, jaise barsaat mein,  
Kuch itne Haseen hain hum, Haseen hum sath mein

snippet.title: Ittar - Jasmine Sandlas | BPraak | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Desi Melodies
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies is here with the hottest track of the season at the onset of summer, Ittar. Performed by Jasmine Sandlas, the vocal delivery is chilling with Jaani's lyrics that show off the love for her partner over BPraak’s modern-folk composition complemented by the man behind the lens, Arinvdr Khaira. 

This Punjabi banger is all about the Gulabi Queen’s mesmerizing voice taking the centerstage to talk about how she wants to adorn herself with the fragrance of ‘Ittar’ (a traditional Indian perfume) and spread it in every inch of her body so that her love can feel her presence even when she's not there. 

Full of metaphors that highlight the depth of romance, Sandlas touches upon the idea of fate and how they’re destined to be together. The combination of Jaani's layered writing, BPraak's exquisite music, and Arvindr Khaira’s inimitable visual storytelling; this musical bouquet is exactly how Jasmine concludes - “If Ittar had a sound, this would be it."

Listen to ‘Ittar’ on your favourite streaming platform - https://bit.ly/Jasmine_Sandlas_Ittar

Radhakrishn Raasleela- part 405 || Krishn Ki Pratigya  |  Radhakrishn | राधाकृष्ण


►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: Jetha ने मारा Auto में बैठने से पहले Bhide को धक्का | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Holi Special
snippet.description:
Like always, Jethalal shows up late at the meeting held in the Club House. As Iyer suggests that Jethalala should be banned from society meetings, Jethalal starts playing Holi with water guns, beginning with Iyer. Later, after a lot of fun and enjoyment, the meeting starts where Iyer and Popatlal announce that there won’t be any Holi celebrations this year in Gokuldham.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast – Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By – Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #SonyPAL #holi #holispecial #happyholi 

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Watch all the 'Holi Special' clips especially curated for you:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G0mUUtCU8U1fh6FBZKC6ahg

snippet.title: સાઢુનાં ધીંગાણાં || SADHU NA DHINGANA || #RAMTO_JOGI || #KIRAN_KHOKHANI || #KRISHNA_TELEFILMS
snippet.description:
વાલાફુવાની જાનમાં આવેલા અપલખણાં જાનૈયાએ ભીમફુવાની ઘોડીને બીડીનું ઠુંઠુ છાપ્યુ અને ઘોડી થઈ જાડ... અરરર.. પછી ?? પછી જે થયું ઈ જોવા માટે જોઈ લ્યો અમારો રંગીન વિડિયો સાઢુનાં ધીંગાણાં

કિરણ ખોખાણી લિખિત-અભિનિત-નિર્મિત ... સાઢુનાં ધીંગાણાં  યુટ્યુબ ચેનલ રમતો જોગી પર.. નવા-જુના જમાનાની અવનવી વાસ્તવિક વાતુનો રસથાળ અને સાથે સાથે જ્ઞાન ગમ્મતનો એકસ્ટ્રા સંભાર પિરસતી સૌની લોકપ્રિય ચેનલ @RAMTO JOGI આજે જ લાઈક, શેર અને સબસ્ક્રાઈબ કરો

"To get more updates Subscribe to our YouTube Channel "Ramto Jogi" and follow us on 
Youtube : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGxe...

snippet.title: Pakistan Holi : पाकिस्तान के Karachi में कैसे मनाई गई होली, क्या बोला हिंदू समुदाय? (BBC Hindi)
snippet.description:
पाकिस्तान के कराची शहर में हर साल की तरह इस बार भी हिंदू समुदाय ने रंगों का त्योहार होली धूमधाम से मनाया. हालांकि, देश में आसमान छू रही महंगाई का असर होली पर भी नज़र आया. कराची शहर से बीबीसी संवाददाता शुमाइला ख़ान की रिपोर्ट.

#Pakistan #PakistanHoli #Holi

* जिन खबरों, तस्वीरों और दावों पर आपको हो शक, हम आपके लिए करेंगे उनकी परख. बीबीसी फ़ैक्ट चेक है आपके साथ. बस भेजिए WhatsApp मैसेज 9811520111 पर. बीबीसी फ़ैक्ट चेक यानी सच की कसौटी.

* Corona Virus से जुड़े और दिलचस्प वीडियो देखने के लिए यहां क्लिक करें : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=npgvIvfmNkE&list=PLYxuvEJLss6ByutcqkthikPxV3ccUkwPB

* कोरोना वायरस से जुड़ी सारी प्रामाणिक ख़बरें पढ़ने के लिए क्लिक करें : https://www.bbc.com/hindi/international-51848794

* ऐसे ही और दिलचस्प वीडियो देखने के लिए चैनल सब्सक्राइब ज़रूर करें-
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCN7B-QD0Qgn2boVH5Q0pOWg?disable_polymer=true

snippet.title: A Gold Coin Winner At Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Throwback
snippet.description:
Episode 1499: A Gold Coin Winner At Gokuldham 
--------------------
Daya chastises Jetha for consuming so much tea. Jetha defends his behaviour by praising Daya's tea-brewing skills. Daya is taken aback by Jetha's flattering methods. Later, the men of Gokuldhum argue vehemently about earning a gold coin. Who was fortunate this time? Follow along!

Show Name- Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast -  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Shailesh Lodha
Full Episode - 1499
Produced By - Asit Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #SAB

Click here to Subscribe to SAB Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

Click to watch all the episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7a6aWvIzLwbDe6FzzowRhMq

Aise mein Geet milti hai Maan se, jo Dev ka hi Bhai hai, lekin Donon hi apne is rishte se anjaan hain. Maan ki madad se Geet apni ek nayi zindagi shuroo karti hai aur donon mein pyaar ho jaata hai. Dekhiye kaise saari kadvi Sachchaaiyon se joojhte huye, donon ka rishta aage baddhta hai.


#GeetHuiSabseParayi #starbharat #drishtidhami
